channel.title: How can i remove a custim log in background?
channel.description: Can some please tell me how to delete a custom log in background EX. The old runescape background had 2 ttouren like monsters when summoning first came out. Please help

item.title: How can i remove a custim log in background?
item.dc:creator: @Svitkona Svitkona
item.description:
@Svitkona wrote:

i don’t think you can remove it, but you can replace it. if you check your client files, you’ll probably see a jpg file called “XXXXscape.jpg” or something close to that. now replace it and compile, and there you go.
